data.name: customSqlQuery3.Sql
data.value: select "M_Board_Member"."Board_Id", "Employee"."Employee_Name_Ar", "M_Member_Type"."Member_Type_Name_Ar", "M_Board_Member"."Member_Type_Id", "M_Attendees"."Attendess_Status", CASE WHEN "M_Attendees"."Attendess_Status" = 1 THEN 'حاضر' ELSE 'غائب' END as Status, "M_Attendees"."Meeting_Id", "M_Meeting"."Meeting_Id" from ((((("dbo"."M_Board_Member" "M_Board_Member" inner join "dbo"."M_Board" "M_Board" on ("M_Board"."Board_Id" = "M_Board_Member"."Board_Id")) inner join "dbo"."Employee" "Employee" on ("Employee"."Employee_Id" = "M_Board_Member"."Employee_Id")) inner join "dbo"."M_Meeting" "M_Meeting" on ("M_Meeting"."Board_Id" = "M_Board"."Board_Id")) inner join "dbo"."M_Member_Type" "M_Member_Type" on ("M_Member_Type"."Member_Type_Id" = "M_Board_Member"."Member_Type_Id")) Left join "dbo"."M_Attendees" "M_Attendees" on (("M_Attendees"."Board_Member_Id" = "M_Board_Member"."Board_Member_Id") and ("M_Attendees"."Meeting_Id" = "M_Meeting"."Meeting_Id"))) where "M_Meeting"."Meeting_Id" =@Meeting_Id

select "M_Board_Member"."Board_Member_Id", "M_Board_Member"."Board_Id", "Employee"."Employee_Name_Ar", "M_Member_Type"."Member_Type_Name_Ar", "M_Meeting"."Meeting_Id", "M_Recommendation"."Recommendation_Status", CASE WHEN "M_Recommendation"."Recommendation_Status" = 1 THEN 'موافق' WHEN "M_Recommendation"."Recommendation_Status" = 2 THEN 'متحفظ' WHEN "M_Recommendation"."Recommendation_Status" = 3 THEN 'غير موافق' WHEN "M_Recommendation"."Recommendation_Status" = 4 THEN 'موافق' WHEN "M_Recommendation"."Recommendation_Status" = 5 THEN 'غير موافق' END as Status, "M_Recommendation"."Recommendation_Description" from ((((("dbo"."M_Board_Member" "M_Board_Member" inner join "dbo"."M_Board" "M_Board" on ("M_Board"."Board_Id" = "M_Board_Member"."Board_Id")) inner join "dbo"."M_Meeting" "M_Meeting" on ("M_Meeting"."Board_Id" = "M_Board"."Board_Id")) inner join "dbo"."Employee" "Employee" on ("Employee"."Employee_Id" = "M_Board_Member"."Employee_Id")) inner join "dbo"."M_Member_Type" "M_Member_Type" on ("M_Member_Type"."Member_Type_Id" = "M_Board_Member"."Member_Type_Id")) left join "dbo"."M_Recommendation" "M_Recommendation" on (("M_Recommendation"."Board_Member_Id" = "M_Board_Member"."Board_Member_Id") and ("M_Recommendation"."Meeting_Id" = "M_Meeting"."Meeting_Id")))
where "M_Meeting"."Meeting_Id" =@Meeting_Id
